metadata.name: KEK PEPE BALLOON
metadata.description:
Memes save the world!💚For the culture!🙏

This is FANART Nyan Balloon 🎨 Created 2023 by SASHA CHUDO 🐸 Respect & Big Thanks for Inspiration to ☆Chris☆ @PRguitarman🎈

This is burn token. You'll have the option to exchange your Kek Pepe Balloon for a new piece in next 48 hours. Then in next 2-3 days new Kek Balloon character will appear. After 24 hours the Kek character is sealed, and a new character will take its place in next 2-3 days. Please check @ChudoSasshha Twitter page above for more details.
